description:
For an international project in Chennai, we are urgently looking for a Hybrid Python Developer to design and develop pipelines and programs by using Python language.










 We are looking for a motivated contractor. Candidates need to be fluent in English.










**Tasks and responsibilities:** 



* Design, Develop and implement new Python pipelines, programs/applications, and prototypes;
* Integrate applications with external APIs, web services and legacy data sources;
* Estimate Design, Build, Test and implementation level of effort based upon requirements and design;
* Write Python programs for comparing file types and for processing different file formats viz. Json, XML, CSV, XLS etc;
* The project\\-focused Developer will work with the PM in developing python scripts for analyzing, comparing files, build integration;
* Develop Python scripts, trouble shoot/ fix existing scripts and tools, with focus on automation, integration and visualization;









**Profile:** 



* Bachelor or Master degree;
* \\+5 years of relevant experience in design, build and development of Python based applications and programs;
* In\\-depth theoretical understanding and practical expertise regarding enterprise Information Management Systems;
* Ability to work individually, given a task/ problem, without having to rely for guidance in Python programming;
* Collaborate closely with other Python developers, on a need basis;
* Extensive understanding and knowledge of various python libraries like Pandas, NumPy, Scikit, Beautiful Soup, Matplotlib etc;
* Troubleshooting \\& performance tuning of Python programs/ applications;
* All phases of software development life cycle including analysis, design, implementation, testing and deployment;
* Strong Object\\-Oriented Program design and implementation skills;
* Strong Knowledge of Relational Databases, preferably Azure SQL, Oracle PL/SQL, and design concepts;
* Fluent in English;
